{
  "stem": "2004.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And for us, every day that we were under the occupation or in camp, it felt like a year.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Basically, a day can be a long time if you are under stress.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was under stress, every minute of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were in that camp, in that lumber yard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we worked in that lumber yard, continuing our things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our friends next door, which was the tar paper factory, they worked in the paper factory, in that tar paper factory.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stayed and worked in that place until, I would say this was-- now we are in-- they have liquidated the ghetto in Gorlice in August of 1942.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We continue working in that place until sometimes in I think it must've been either December of 1942 or possibly January of 1943.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the way, my cousin who was Jacob's youngest son, who was with my aunt, he at the time was working.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was very mechanically inclined.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he was-- he got himself a job repairing automobiles for the German army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was actually working for the German army in their garages as a-- he was a young man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was, I think, two years older than me, maybe a year or two years older.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was quite mechanically inclined.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he was able to-- and he was already working for several months there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he and his mother were able to-- what happened is when the-- when the ghetto was liquidated, his mother was able to be put into the paper factory, the paper factory, that tar paper factory.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
